      <span style="font-size:13px;line-height:14px;font-weight:300;font-family:nyt-franklin, arial, sans-serif;border-top-left-radius:4px;border-top-right-radius:4px;border-bottom-right-radius:4px;border-bottom-left-radius:4px;transition:background-color 0.3s;-webkit-transition:background-color 0.3s;display:inline-block;margin:0px 5px 0px 0px;padding:7px 9px;border:0px;color:rgb(255, 255, 255);cursor:pointer;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(153, 153, 153);text-align:center;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;width:auto;min-width:65px;margin-bottom:5px;">Owner or supervisor</span>
